{"data":[{"date":"15:42 14/07","title":"Ronaldo v\u00e0 Benzema s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau \u1edf Serie A?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/27/ronaldo-va-benzema-sap-doi-dau-nhau-o-serie-a.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Karim Benzema c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, HLV Carlo Ancelotti \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n San Paolo.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Benzema</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Carlo Ancelotti \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay th\u1ebf Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Napoli t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Paolo m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Karim Benzema c\u1ee7a Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Karim Benzema c\u1ee7a Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/Napoli-muon-mua-Karim-Benzema-cua-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Benzema</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAncelotti \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Karim Benzema c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, HLV Carlo Ancelotti \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n San Paolo.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Benzema lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ghi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng anh l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Ancelotti \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Benzema v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Napoli chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987. Theo La Sexta, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-real-xac-nhan-ronaldo-cap-ben-juventus-180-190888.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span>, n\u1ebfu Benzema c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Napoli, hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nhau \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Napoli c\u00f3 Benzema</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef Ronaldo \u1edf l\u1ea1i, vi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Benzema mo ty so sau sai sot cua Karius\" title=\"Benzema m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 sau sai s\u00f3t c\u1ee7a Karius\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/ronaldo-va-benzema-sap-doi-dau-nhau-o-serie-a.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea3 Benzema cho Napoli</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Ronaldo l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00eanh m\u00f4ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Los Blancos, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef Benzema, Isco, Bale hay Asensio. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Napoli ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao 31 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u00e2n HLV Lopetegui c\u1ee7a Real kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Benzema v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1255","checkdouble":"191165"},{"date":"15:48 14/07","title":"\"Gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft\" xong Conte, Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n li\u1ec1n 3 t\u00e2n binh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/che.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m t\u00e2n HLV Sarri, v\u00e0 Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n 3 t\u00e2n binh trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><h2>Chelsea b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00fac m\u1eafc k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c sa th\u1ea3i Antonio Conte. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf, \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi. Nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00ecnh tr\u1ec7 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 The Blues chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n tin vui t\u1edbi t\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho t\u1eeb Napoli, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB Italia \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, khi th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;s\u1ed1ng l\u1ed7i&rdquo; v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb nhi\u1ec1u ti\u00ean h\u01a1n c\u1ee7a Chelsea. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 Jorginho, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp theo, ngay sau khi World Cup 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London s\u1ebd l\u00e0m r\u00f5 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 - Thibaut Coutois v\u00e0 Eden Hazard. Song song v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111em v\u1ec1 2 t\u00e2n binh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, thay th\u1ebf ch\u00ednh 2 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n 3 t\u00e2n binh ngay khi b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri\" title=\"Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n 3 t\u00e2n binh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/che.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n 3 t\u00e2n binh ngay khi b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi The Blues ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, v\u00e0 Chelsea kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00eam d\u00e0i l\u1eafm m\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111em s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1edbi AS Roma \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi mua Alisson Becker, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Chelsea l\u00e0 CLB m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ng\u1ef1a v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, sau khi Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat lui \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang&hellip; Courtois.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Golovin s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay m\u1ed9t trong hai tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t l\u00e0 Eden Hazard ho\u1eb7c Willian, v\u00e0 Golovin s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng sau s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n 3 t\u00e2n binh, m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111ang s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-chinh-thuc-bo-nhiem-nguoi-thay-the-conte-172-191167.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/cuc-nong-chelsea-chinh-thuc-bo-nhiem-nguoi-thay-the-conte.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-chinh-thuc-bo-nhiem-nguoi-thay-the-conte-172-191167.html\">C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: Chelsea CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Conte</span><br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c The Blues x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn, trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-chelsea-sa-thai-hlv-antonio-conte-465-191114.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/chinh-thuc-chelsea-sa-thai-hlv-antonio-conte.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-chelsea-sa-thai-hlv-antonio-conte-465-191114.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte</span><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia kh\u00e1c t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge trong giai...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-neu-hlv-sarri-dan-dat-chelsea-thay-conte-172-191110.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-neu-hlv-sarri-dan-dat-chelsea-thay-conte.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-neu-hlv-sarri-dan-dat-chelsea-thay-conte-172-191110.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu HLV Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte</span><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea thay Conte ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n s\u00e2n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1254","checkdouble":"191166"},{"date":"15:23 14/07","title":"C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: Chelsea CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Conte","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/cuc-nong-chelsea-chinh-thuc-bo-nhiem-nguoi-thay-the-conte.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Roma b\u00e1n Alisson n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Alisson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Serie A. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Brazil c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roma b\u00e1n Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Roma b\u00e1n Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/Roma-ban-Alisson-voi-gia-50-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn h\u1ecfi mua Alisson\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil gi\u00fap anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-thu-mon-moi-voi-gia-sieu-khung-180-182517.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alisson</span>, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Navas, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 32.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m Alisson, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Braizl th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Karuis, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Roma. Vi\u1ec7c Thibaut Courtois t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Roma s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Alisson</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Roma b\u00e1n Alisson n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/roma-bao-tin-vui-cho-real-vu-thu-mon-alisson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roma h\u1ea1 gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGianLuca Di Marzio.com kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Roma ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn h\u1ea1 gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o ch\u1ecbu chi ra 45 \u0111\u1ebfn 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ee7 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Alisson.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 Alisson nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Chelsea, Liverpool ho\u1eb7c Real ph\u1ea3i \u201cph\u00e1 k\u00e9t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eeba tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb World Cup 2018, Brazil c\u1ee7a Alisson \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay khi d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 anh v\u1eabn kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Roma v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia c\u00f3 to\u00e0n quy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1253","checkdouble":"191167"},{"date":"15:36 14/07","title":"Rakitic s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1ea1 l\u00f9ng n\u1ebfu Croatia v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/rakitic-san-sang-lam-dieu-la-lung-neu-croatia-vo-dich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Zlatko Dalic l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Rakitic s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111i x\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2>Rakitic \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c \u0110T Croatia c\u0169ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai (15/7), v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o s\u1ecdc ca-ro l\u1eadp n\u00ean chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 theo Ivan Rakitic, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Croatia \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, anh \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Barca s\u1ebd x\u0103m m\u00ecnh, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea5y chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u00e2ng, t\u00f4i \u0111ang ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111i x\u0103m&rdquo; &ndash; Ivan Rakitic chia s\u1ebb. &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh x\u0103m&hellip; \u1edf tr\u00e1n. B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5y, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u1edf \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecfi v\u1ee3 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rakitic s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111i x\u0103m \u1edf tr\u00e1n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup\" title=\"Rakitic s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111i x\u0103m \u1edf tr\u00e1n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/rakitic-san-sang-lam-dieu-la-lung-neu-croatia-vo-dich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rakitic s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111i x\u0103m \u1edf tr\u00e1n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, \u0111\u1eebng b\u1eadn t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Croatia.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u1ea9ng cao, v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n h\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft, ni\u1ec1m ki\u00eau h\u00e3nh, th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y&rdquo; &ndash; Rakitic k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng. V\u00e0 trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Croatia l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111ang mong ch\u1edd li\u1ec7u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Rakitic s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111i x\u0103m nh\u01b0 anh chia s\u1ebb hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-fairplay-gui-loi-chuc-chien-thang-den-ca-phap-va-croatia-421-191144.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/neymar-fairplay-gui-loi-chuc-chien-thang-den-ca-phap-va-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-fairplay-gui-loi-chuc-chien-thang-den-ca-phap-va-croatia-421-191144.html\">Neymar g\u1eedi t\u00e2m th\u01b0 ch\u00fac chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Croatia</span><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u01a1n, ng\u00f4i sao Brazil nh\u1eafn nh\u1ee7 Kylian Mbappe v\u00e0 Ivan Rakitic khi hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 c\u1ee7a anh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u trong tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-chuyen-toi-ngoai-hang-anh-421-191158.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/hlv-croatia-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-chuyen-toi-ngoai-hang-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-chuyen-toi-ngoai-hang-anh-421-191158.html\">HLV Croatia n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh?</span><br>\r\nHLV Zlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1252","checkdouble":"191168"},{"date":"15:59 14/07","title":"Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Eden Hazard cho Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/real-madrid-chot-gia-ban-eden-hazard-cho-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea b\u00e1n Eden Hazard cho Real Madrid n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Mirror \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real chi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef Ronaldo \u1edf l\u1ea1i, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Ronaldo k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus, anh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea b\u00e1n Eden Hazard cho Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea b\u00e1n Eden Hazard cho Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/real-madrid-chot-gia-ban-eden-hazard-cho-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real chi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Eden Hazard\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real Madrid l\u00e0 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo, Mbappe v\u00e0 Neymar l\u00e0 2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, song PSG h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i 400 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Neymar v\u00e0 290 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Mbappe.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 cho hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd nh\u1eafm m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb h\u01a1n. H\u00f4m qua, Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-san-sang-chi-150-trieu-bang-de-mua-hazard-180-191070.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nh\u1ecf, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Los Blancos.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Hazard cho Real v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea b\u00e1n Eden Hazard cho Real Madrid n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Mirror \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard Chelsea\" title=\"Eden Hazard Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/hazard-nen-tu-choi-real-de-tro-thanh-huyen-thoai-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Eden Hazard v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Sarri m\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Chelsea thay Conte, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 400.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3\u00a0thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Hazard t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Real Madrid. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 Real s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 Hazard ra \u0111i Chelsea s\u1ebd nh\u1eafm Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a MU thay th\u1ebf, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1251","checkdouble":"191169"},{"date":"17:04 14/07","title":"Roma b\u00e1o tin vui cho Real v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/24/roma-bao-tin-vui-cho-real-vu-thu-mon-alisson.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Roma b\u00e1n Alisson n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Alisson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Serie A. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Brazil c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roma b\u00e1n Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Roma b\u00e1n Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/Roma-ban-Alisson-voi-gia-50-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn h\u1ecfi mua Alisson\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil gi\u00fap anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-thu-mon-moi-voi-gia-sieu-khung-180-182517.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alisson</span>, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Navas, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 32.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m Alisson, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Braizl th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Karuis, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Roma. Vi\u1ec7c Thibaut Courtois t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Roma s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Alisson</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Roma b\u00e1n Alisson n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/roma-bao-tin-vui-cho-real-vu-thu-mon-alisson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roma h\u1ea1 gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGianLuca Di Marzio.com kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Roma ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn h\u1ea1 gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o ch\u1ecbu chi ra 45 \u0111\u1ebfn 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ee7 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Alisson.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 Alisson nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Chelsea, Liverpool ho\u1eb7c Real ph\u1ea3i \u201cph\u00e1 k\u00e9t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eeba tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb World Cup 2018, Brazil c\u1ee7a Alisson \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay khi d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 anh v\u1eabn kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Roma v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia c\u00f3 to\u00e0n quy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1250","checkdouble":"191170"},{"date":"16:02 14/07","title":"Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, Gareth Bale x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/ngay-hom-nay-gareth-bale-xac-dinh-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho bi\u1ebft, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Gareth Bale x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0o h\u00f4m nay, sau cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 v\u1edbi HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Julen Lopetegui.\r\n</h2><h2>Bale s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 1 trong 2 ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai (c\u00f9ng Cris Ronaldo) ngay sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1, Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi Real Madrid. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 no n\u00ea danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp. Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, anh \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, v\u00e0 \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i tho\u00e1t cho s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay Los Blancos \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juve, theo \u0111u\u1ed5i cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u m\u1edbi. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn t\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale, r\u1eb1ng anh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ea5y v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao nh\u1ea5t, hay ra \u0111i theo ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ng\u00f4i sao x\u1ee9 Wales cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Real, nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i chia s\u1ebb t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, trong khi t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Bale x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sau khi c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi HLV Lopetegui\" title=\"Gareth Bale x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/ngay-hom-nay-gareth-bale-xac-dinh-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gareth Bale x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sau khi c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi HLV Lopetegui</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng mong \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1eaft \u0111\u1ee9t li\u00ean l\u1ea1c. Th\u00fa th\u1ef1c, t\u00f4i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng xem l\u1ea1i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ra h\u01b0\u1edbng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t&rdquo; &ndash; Gareth Bale chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, HLV Lopetegui l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Isco v\u00e0 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n cho Lucas Vazquez, hay Marco Asensio. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Gareth Bale x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ra \u0111i, Premier League v\u00e0 Man United ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 Wales. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Bale, v\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1edd m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-gia-nhap-real-madrid-voi-gia-ky-luc-180-191140.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-gia-nhap-real-madrid-voi-gia-ky-luc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-gia-nhap-real-madrid-voi-gia-ky-luc-180-191140.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Hazard gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV Roberto Martinez xoay quanh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-ra-thong-bao-ve-thuong-vu-neymar-180-191138.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-ra-thong-bao-ve-thuong-vu-neymar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-ra-thong-bao-ve-thuong-vu-neymar-180-191138.html\">Real Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Neymar</span><br>\r\nTrang ch\u1ee7 CLB ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng b\u00e0i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao Neymar t\u1eeb Paris Saint-Germain.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1249","checkdouble":"191171"},{"date":"15:59 14/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn tranh gi\u1ea3i 3 B\u1ec9 vs Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/du-doan-anh-vs-bi-va-nhan-dinh-soi-keo-ty-le-bi-vs-anh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 vs Anh v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110T Anh khi h\u1ecd \u1edf trong t\u00e2m l\u00fd tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- \u0110T Anh kh\u00f4ng thua <br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Anh th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 B\u1ec9 vs Anh</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: B\u1ec9 vs Anh<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi gian: 21h ng\u00e0y 14/7<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: S\u00e2n Saint-Petersburg<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: B\u1ec9 1.01*0:1/4*0.94 Anh<br>\r\nTBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: Nhi\u1ec1u 1.06*3*0.87 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 vs Anh v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, soi k\u00e8o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 vs Anh v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, soi k\u00e8o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/du-doan-anh-vs-bi-va-nhan-dinh-soi-keo-ty-le-bi-vs-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 vs Anh 21h ng\u00e0y 14/7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n\u0110T Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 non n\u1edbt l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Croatia n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 World Cup 2018 n\u00f3i chung. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u00ecn c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh, Tam s\u01b0 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u1ea1c quan. H\u1ecd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o World Cup 2018 th\u1ef1c ra kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1eeba do th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, v\u1eeba do \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ednh ra, \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf trung b\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Gareth Southgate d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111i t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Anh\" title=\"\u0110T Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/roy-keane-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia-la-cu-soc-voi-nhieu-nguoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110T Anh thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia, HLV Southgate \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p sai l\u1ea7m cho Anh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, sau khi c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5 c\u1ee7a Kieran Trippier, Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3m t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Croatia qu\u1eadt d\u1eady. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn b\u1edfi d\u00e0n tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 non kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt kh\u00e1c nhau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 v\u1edbi B\u1ec9, c\u00e1i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd kh\u00e1c. T\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3. Khi \u0111\u00f3, Anh m\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u m\u0169i c\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u t\u00e0u tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Anh kh\u00f4ng ai kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i Harry Kane. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi 6 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. Sau b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Kane \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane tiep tuc ghi ban\" title=\"Harry Kane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/harry-kane-la-so-9-toan-dien-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Harry Kane \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng Anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Kane. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 qu\u00e1 s\u00e2u v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n. Tr\u00e1i l\u1ea1i, \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3, khi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Anh d\u00e2ng cao, Kane c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e0i s\u0103n b\u00e0n \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua c\u1ee7a Kane l\u00e0 ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c v\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb n\u1eefa c\u1ee7a anh trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 vs Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Kane. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u1ed9t khi c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 9 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, Anh lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 B\u1ec9. \u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p Tam s\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- \u0110T Anh kh\u00f4ng thua (+1/4)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Anh th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLong Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1248","checkdouble":"191172"},{"date":"16:22 14/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP B\u1ec9 vs Anh 21h00 ng\u00e0y 14/7 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/truc-tiep-bi-vs-anh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp B\u1ec9 vs Anh: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 14/7.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp B\u1ec9 vs Anh: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 14/7.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-bi-vs-anh-463-191173.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP B\u1ec8 VS ANH</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1247","checkdouble":"191173"},{"date":"16:40 14/07","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh: D\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, Premier League c\u0169ng th\u1eafng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/14/truoc-tran-bi-vs-anh-du-the-nao-premier-league-cung-thang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u1ec9 vs Anh c\u0169ng \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c cho c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a 2 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 h\u1ecd li\u00ean t\u1ee5c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Eden Hazard v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i chia s\u1ebb, chi l\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c &ldquo;m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3&rdquo; \u1edf ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u, ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 ngo\u00e0i 20. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0110T Ph\u00e1p qu\u00e1 d\u00e0y d\u1ea1n kinh nghi\u1ec7m &ndash; d\u00f9 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb. G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng Gaulois \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0110T B\u1ec9 b\u1edfi c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n, m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 1-0.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh D\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, Premier League c\u0169ng th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh D\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, Premier League c\u0169ng th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Truoc-tran-Bi-vs-Anh-Du-the-nao,-Premier-League-cung-thang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T Anh c\u0169ng g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Croatia \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u00f3a gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 \u0111em c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0. H\u1ecd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0110T Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u0103ng s\u1ee9c trong 240 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3, Tam S\u01b0 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau c\u00f9ng, b\u1edfi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u00f9ng kinh nghi\u1ec7m non n\u1edbt. H\u1ecd qu\u00e1 sai l\u1ea7m khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, kh\u00f4ng tung ra \u0111\u00f2n k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 Croatia l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi v\u1eady, thay v\u00ec ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nhau trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 2 \u0111\u1ed9i &ndash; gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y B\u1ec9 vs Anh \u0111\u00e0nh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c &ndash; tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3. Ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 2 thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n t\u1ea5u h\u00e0i n\u1eefa, sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng (2 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u01b0\u1eddng nhau v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh D\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, Premier League c\u0169ng th\u1eafng \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110T Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/roy-keane-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia-la-cu-soc-voi-nhieu-nguoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean thu\u1ed9c Premier League, B\u1ec9 vs Anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng &ndash; d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch nh\u1ea5t, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t nh\u1eefng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Brazil, Ph\u00e1p, Argentina ho\u1eb7c B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. B\u1ec9 vs Anh d\u00f9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfu d\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng ai k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh ban \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t s\u00e2u v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Roberto Martinez t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng 1/8, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd b\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n &ndash; trong \u0111\u00f3 pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 di\u1ec5n ra trong v\u00f2ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn 10 gi\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Brazil ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, B\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3a ch\u1eb7t Neymar, v\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd g\u1ed3m Hazard &ndash; De Bruyne &ndash; Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh D\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, Premier League c\u0169ng th\u1eafng \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"De Bruyne Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/101748-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T B\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0110T Anh, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ebfn L\u0110B\u0110 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft r\u1ed3i v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. N\u1ebfu ai \u0111\u00f3 cho r\u1eb1ng Tam S\u01b0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, ch\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n s\u1ebd b\u1ecb c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t, b\u1edfi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00f4ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Argentina, Brazil hay T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Nh\u01b0ng trong khi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u1eabn l\u1ea7m l\u0169i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn m\u1ed9t.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-5-2 c\u00e1ch t\u00e2n, ph\u00e1 b\u1ecf truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng 4-4-2, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi v\u1eabn gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec tinh t\u00fay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u, d\u00e0n s\u01b0 t\u1eed tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Gareth Southgate th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 g\u00e2y qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh (\u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c) nh\u1ea5t trong 32 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T B\u1ec9 2 l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft trong 2 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i xa h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, khi \u0110T B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00ednh \u0111\u00e1nh thu\u00ea, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf n\u0103m nay c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft l\u1edbn v\u1edbi n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t 9/11 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Anh. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Tam S\u01b0 d\u00f9 g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 non tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB Premier League ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh D\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, Premier League c\u0169ng th\u1eafng \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Henderson c\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Panama 6-1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/Anh-&ndash;-Bi-tinh&hellip;-nhuong-nhau-thang-Dung-bien-minh-thanh-con-tin-cua-su-may-rui!-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tuy\u1ec3n Anh c\u0169ng tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nC\u00e1c C\u0110V s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a La Liga trong 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, v\u1edbi 9/10 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u (Champions League, Europa League) thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Nh\u01b0ng h\u00e3y nh\u00ecn xem \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n x\u1ee9 s\u1edf b\u00f2 t\u00f3t \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y? C\u00f2n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n La Liga c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 tho\u00e1i tr\u00e0o, khi CR7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Premier League v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1edd th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 &quot;\u0111\u0103ng phong&quot;, khi m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u1ec9 vs Anh v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, cho d\u00f9 b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 \u0111i ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa, Premier League c\u0169ng l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u01a1n m\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bi-vs-anh-21h00-ngay-147-moi-nguoi-vi-mot-nguoi-421-191141.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/Bi-vs-Anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bi-vs-anh-21h00-ngay-147-moi-nguoi-vi-mot-nguoi-421-191141.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Anh (21h00 ng\u00e0y 14/7): M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00ec m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a nh\u01b0 tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup, c\u1ea3 B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Anh c\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong th\u1ebf ng\u1ea9ng cao \u0111\u1ea7u,...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-doan-anh-vs-bi-va-nhan-dinh-soi-keo-ty-le-bi-vs-anh-184-191172.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/du-doan-anh-vs-bi-va-nhan-dinh-soi-keo-ty-le-bi-vs-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-doan-anh-vs-bi-va-nhan-dinh-soi-keo-ty-le-bi-vs-anh-184-191172.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn tranh gi\u1ea3i 3 B\u1ec9 vs Anh</span><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 vs Anh v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110T Anh khi h\u1ecd \u1edf trong t\u00e2m l\u00fd tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1246","checkdouble":"191175"},{"date":"09:32 14/07","title":"\"Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p qu\u00ean chung k\u1ebft EURO 2016\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/umtiti-phap-khong-duoc-phep-quen-chung-ket-euro-2016.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti cho r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00ean nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft EURO 2016.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh khi l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn trong hai n\u0103m qua. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i EURO 2016, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Croatia song trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra t\u1ea1i \u1edf chung k\u1ebft Euro hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p qu\u00ean EURO 2016 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p qu\u00ean EURO 2016 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/5/umtiti-phap-khong-duoc-phep-quen-chung-ket-euro-2016.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Umtiti (22) mu\u1ed1n tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng trong tr\u1eadn\u00a0chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Umtiti n\u00f3i: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 sai \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Euro 2016 \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m. Croatia l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nghi\u00eam t\u00fac nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 Ivan Rakitic v\u00e0 Luka Modric, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: \"\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng cho Croatia. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf ba tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 Croatia c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. H\u1ecd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed3ng quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti, Paul Pogba c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7: \u201cT\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 nu\u1ed1t tr\u00f4i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c thua m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 n\u00f3 r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf EURO 2016. Khi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin ch\u1eafc s\u1ebd th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 d\u1eb7n nhau kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea1m ph\u1ea3i sai l\u1ea7m n\u0103m x\u01b0a\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 22h00 t\u1ed1i mai 15/7 (gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam).</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-hlv-simeone-dua-ra-loi-khuyen-cho-griezmann-421-191147.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-hlv-simeone-dua-ra-loi-khuyen-cho-griezmann.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-hlv-simeone-dua-ra-loi-khuyen-cho-griezmann-421-191147.html\">Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: HLV Simeone \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean cho Griezmann</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai 15/7, HLV Diego Simeone \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Griezmann \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/modric-toi-san-sang-doi-3-cup-c1-de-vo-dich-world-cup-469-191113.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/modric-toi-san-sang-doi-3-cup-c1-de-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/modric-toi-san-sang-doi-3-cup-c1-de-vo-dich-world-cup-469-191113.html\">Modric: T\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i 4 c\u00fap C1 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Modric kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi anh. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u00f2n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u Champions...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ivan-perisic-tiet-lo-ly-do-giup-croatia-co-the-danh-bai-phap-421-191086.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/ivan-perisic-tiet-lo-ly-do-giup-croatia-co-the-danh-bai-phap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ivan-perisic-tiet-lo-ly-do-giup-croatia-co-the-danh-bai-phap-421-191086.html\">Ivan Perisic ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Croatia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p</span><br>\r\nIvan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Les Bleus trong tr\u1eadn chung...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/croatia-truoc-tran-gap-phap-tinh-than-co-khoa-lap-yeu-to-the-luc-421-191115.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/croatia-truoc-tran-gap-phap-tinh-than-co-khoa-lap-yeu-to-the-luc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/croatia-truoc-tran-gap-phap-tinh-than-co-khoa-lap-yeu-to-the-luc-421-191115.html\">Croatia tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p: Tinh th\u1ea7n c\u00f3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c?</span><br>\r\nCroatia \u0111\u00e3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup, tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#333333;mso-fareast-language:=\"\" ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1245","checkdouble":"191148"},{"date":"10:52 14/07","title":"HLV Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Shaqiri c\u1ee7a Liverpool?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-ve-tan-binh-shaqiri-cua-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c sau khi Liverpool ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 t\u1eeb Stoke City v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 13,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-xherdan-shaqiri-172-191137.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri</span> sau khi k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 13,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Stoke City.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield v\u00e0 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 23 quen thu\u1ed9c. Anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 ba gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau hai qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ea3 tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa - Naby Keita t\u1eeb RB Leipzig v\u00e0 Fabinho t\u1eeb Monaco.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Shaqiri t\u00e2n binh Liverpool h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Shaqiri t\u00e2n binh Liverpool h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-ve-tan-binh-shaqiri-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Jurgen Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Shaqiri, t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong h\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">HLV Jurgen Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Shaqiri, t\u00e2n binh h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng trong c\u00f4ng cu\u1ed9c d\u1ef1ng x\u00e2y \u0111\u1ebf ch\u1ebf The Kop: \u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Xherdan h\u1ebft.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n \u1edf Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf \u0110\u1ee9c, quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m Premier League v\u00e0 g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ee7 bi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 v\u1eefng \u1edf m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t n\u00e0y. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u1eefa.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cXherdan s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n \u2013 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh v\u00e0 li\u1ec1u l\u0129nh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f3 tin tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t cho Liverpool khi linh ho\u1ea1t v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i tin ch\u1eafc v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi, Xherdan s\u1ebd h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 th\u00edch nghi nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u1edbi Liverpool m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Anfield ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u1eadt d\u1eady tr\u1ea7m tr\u1ed3, v\u1ed7 tay t\u00e1n th\u01b0\u1edfng trong m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-xherdan-shaqiri-172-191137.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/chinh-thuc-liverpool-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-xherdan-shaqiri.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-xherdan-shaqiri-172-191137.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri</span><br>\r\nLiverpool ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 Xherdan Shaqiri sau khi k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 13,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Stoke...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1244","checkdouble":"191149"},{"date":"09:23 14/07","title":"Shaqiri h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Salah","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/shaqiri-hao-huc-truoc-co-hoi-da-cap-cung-salah.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Shaqiri t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Mohamed Salah t\u1ea1i Liverpool \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>Shaqiri h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f9ng Salah</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Salah c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Basel sau khi Shaqiri r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. C\u1ea3 hai ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng nhau trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 nh\u01b0ng Shaqiri c\u0169ng c\u00f3 k\u00fd \u1ee9c v\u1ec1 si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-xherdan-shaqiri-172-191137.html\" target=\"_blank\">Shaqiri \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 13.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span> t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u00e0 Stoke. Trong b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft, Shaqiri t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng Salah \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Shaqiri h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Shaqiri h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/shaqiri-hao-huc-truoc-co-hoi-da-cap-cung-salah.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Shaqiri \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Salah t\u1ea1i Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft anh \u1ea5y qu\u00e1 r\u00f5 nh\u01b0ng anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c khi t\u00f4i c\u00f2n \u1edf Basel. Anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n 2 hay 3 l\u1ea7n g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u1eadp v\u1edbi anh \u1ea5y. Sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec t\u00f4i t\u1edbi Bayern c\u00f2n anh \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i Basel.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5y anh \u1ea5y \u1edf Liverpool. Anh \u1ea5y v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i vui m\u1eebng thay anh \u1ea5y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Salah l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai t\u1ed1t. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec1u mong mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n khi Liverpool kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng n\u0103m nay m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Shaqiri \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn c\u00f9ng Liverpool</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Liverpool t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Bayern. Anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 3 danh hi\u1ec7u V\u0110QG Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 c\u00f9ng Basel. V\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u n\u1eefa \u1edf Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft m\u00f9i v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf Bayern Munich. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0103n ba v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i tin l\u00e0 Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u. C\u00e1c C\u0110V x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f3. Hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-ve-tan-binh-shaqiri-cua-liverpool-172-191149.html\">HLV Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Shaqiri c\u1ee7a Liverpool?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-xherdan-shaqiri-172-191137.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1243","checkdouble":"191150"},{"date":"09:14 14/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 14/7 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/nhan-dinh-hai-phong-vs-binh-duong-17h00-ngay-147-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 14/7 (V\u00f2ng 19 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 147 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 147 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/haiphong-bbd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span>H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: 0-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u1ede giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League 2018, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00edtrong Top 3. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng khi V-League b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c v\u1eeba qua, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Hoa ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ecf to\u00e0n thua 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 8 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng v\u1edbi 23 \u0111i\u1ec3m, h\u01a1n nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi\u1ebfu chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u khi\u1ebfn HLV Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Ho\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 khi c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t m\u1ecfi m\u1ec7t. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i khi h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i t\u1eeb s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, ph\u00f3 m\u1eb7c cho hai ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ngo\u1ea1i binh l\u00e0 Fagan vs Stevens t\u1ef1 x\u1eed l\u00fd. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng \u00edt ra h\u1ecd v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edfnh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00f2a k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh 4-4 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ea3ng Nam trong \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Ti\u1ebfn Linh l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t hattrick.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 kh\u1eafc tinh c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng. Hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng to\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 V-League, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 7 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u1edf L\u1ea1ch Tray (th\u1eafng 4).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN:<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng: V\u0103n L\u00e2m, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Ho\u00e0i D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Ng\u1ecdc T\u00e2n, V\u0103n Ph\u00fa, Qu\u1ed1c Trung, Th\u00e0nh Long, Xu\u00e2n H\u00f9ng, Adriano, Fagan, Stevens.<br>\r\nB\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: T\u1ea5n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, H.T.T\u00e0i, L.T.T\u00e0i, Thanh Th\u1ea3o, Chinedu, Anh T\u00e0i, Ti\u1ebfn Linh, Tanidis, S\u1ef9 Gi\u00e1p, V\u0103n V\u0169, Ho\u00e0ng Max.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1242","checkdouble":"191152"},{"date":"09:17 14/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 14/7: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Colombia t\u1ed1 Barca \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/diem-tin-sang-147-nguoi-hung-colombia-to-barca-doi-xu-te-bac.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Colombia t\u1ed1 Barca \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c, Juve \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Ronaldo, Liverpool s\u1eafp mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 14/7.</h2><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Colombia t\u1ed1 Barca \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yerry Mina \u2013 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o b\u1ecb Barca \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"T\u00f4i nh\u1eadn ra m\u00ecnh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n\u00a0kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean\u00a0trong danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. T\u00f4i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh \u1edf nh\u00e0,\" Mina chia s\u1ebb.\u00a0\"Th\u1eadt\u00a0bu\u1ed3n\u00a0khi ph\u1ea3i\u00a0ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1c\u00a0\u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u qua TV! Ch\u1eb3ng ai mu\u1ed1n\u00a0tr\u1ea3i qua\u00a0c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf\u00a0n\u00e0y\". <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Everton \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Mina v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o\u00a0trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia\u00a0s\u1ebd c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 147 Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Colombia t\u1ed1 Barca \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 147 Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Colombia t\u1ed1 Barca \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Diem-tin-sang-147-Nguoi-hung-Colombia-to-Barca-doi-xu-te-bac-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"width: 779px;\">\r\n            <table style=\"text-align: center; width: 777px;\">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td><em>Mina cho r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u1ea1i Barcelona<br>\r\n                        </em></td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Gianluca Di Mazio c\u1ee7a Sky Sport, Roma \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd h\u1ea1 gi\u00e1 Alisson xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 70 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Liverpool. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao m\u00e0 Roma \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u00e3 bu\u1ed9c L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat lui. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n h\u1ee9ng th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y khi quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Thibaut Courtois c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ra m\u1eaft HLV m\u1edbi<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 sa th\u1ea3i HLV Conte, CLB Chelsea \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ra m\u1eaft HLV ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u1edd Sky Sports Italy \u0111\u01b0a tin HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Brigde. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo c\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n tin, Sarri s\u1ebd k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea trong 2 n\u0103m k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gia h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m. M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng Sarri nh\u1eadn \u1edf Chelsea l\u00e0 5,3 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB, Gianfranco Zola c\u0169ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Sarri tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Juve \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Ronaldo<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italia, CLB Juventus d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd cho ra m\u1eaft Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 16/7 t\u1edbi sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u euro. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Neymar sang PSG n\u1ebfu t\u00ednh t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Real ch\u01b0a c\u1ea7n mua Neymar<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u201cV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin cho r\u1eb1ng CLV li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Neymar c\u1ee7a PSG, Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m r\u00f5 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. PSG v\u00e0 Real c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 m\u1eadt thi\u1ebft. N\u1ebfu Real quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m l\u00e0 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n\u201d, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>M.U mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Maguire<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo\u00a0Daily Mail,\u00a0CLB Man United \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap Anh h\u1ea1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn B\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup. Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 50 tri\u1ec7u B\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Leicester City nh\u1ea3 Maguire.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>HLV Conte c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc ki\u1ec7n Chelsea v\u00ec \"b\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n\" b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo tin t\u1eeb Sky Sport, HLV\u00a0Antonio Conte\u00a0\u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc\u00a0ki\u1ec7n\u00a0CLB Chelsea\u00a0l\u00ean t\u00f2a \u00e1n c\u1ee7a FIFA n\u1ebfu CLB n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu thanh to\u00e1n ph\u00ed b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a\u00a0The Blues\u00a0v\u1eeba\u00a0c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i\u00a0v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.\u00a0Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2019 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. Tuy nhi\u00ean,\u00a0Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n\u00a0b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng.\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam:\u00a0<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-137-mu-co-nguy-co-lon-de-mat-pogba-184-191118.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 13/7: M.U c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Pogba</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Roboto;color:#081F2C\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1241","checkdouble":"191153"}]}